=======================================================================

This software was developed for educational institutions to manage
smart locker systems for equipment lending. It includes components for:

- Mobile applications for end users
- Web administrative dashboard
- Backend API services
- Hardware integration for electronic locks
- Database management and reporting

For commercial use or contributions, please refer to our contribution
guidelines in the project repository.

Contact: suporte@smartlock.suauniversidade.edu.br
Project Repository: https://github.com/sua-universidade/smart-lock-system

